text: Arlo the Alligator Boy is a 2021 American animated movie made by Netflix. It stars the voices of Michael J. Woodard, Mary Lambert, Haley Tju, Jonathan Van Ness, Brett Gelman, Tony Hale, Annie Potts, Flea, Jennifer Coolidge and Vincent Rodriguez III. == Other websites == * * Category:2021 animated movies Category:American animated movies Category:Netflix movies
